{
  "stem": "23410.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And got into the-- a number, and that was all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember like today, we were registered.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was a woman, a Jewish woman, a secretary, who worked also in the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But she worked there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she said to me, you're a young boy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You will not survive here 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Don't you have some kind of a profession that we can put you in in some kind of a professional place, so that you are not in this state and not being beaten every day, and so on.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I worked until the last-- in a month, months, I worked in-- near-- across our house, in this month that I was hiding during the day-- in a chocolate factory, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I worked as an assistant to a glazier.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He had to put in glass in all the windows, because they were bombed out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said-- the first thing I said, I am in wood, lumber.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, lumber's no good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You will be outside all day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You are out to be beaten every day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said, how about a glazier?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She said, that's a good profession, because a glazier's inside, and it will be warmer for you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this is how I became as a glazier.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only trouble was when I said a glazier, and she said, good.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was the only one glazier.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I thought of being an assistant to a glazier, somebody will do the work, and I will help him out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I did not know what to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
